
Instructions on Installing the JOGL Stuff on Your Client Machine:
=================================================================

On Linux:

	* copy the "jogl.jar" file into:

		$JAVA_HOME/jre/lib/ext/

	* copy the libraries "libjogl.so" and "libjogl_cg.so"
		(from the "Linux/" subdirectory) into:

		$JAVA_HOME/jre/lib/i386/

	Note: $JAVA_HOME should be something like:
	
		/opt/sun-jdk-1.5.0.07/

On Windows:

	* copy the "jogl.jar" file into:

		$JAVA_HOME\jre-VERSION\lib\ext\

	* copy the libraries "jogl.dll" and "jogl_cg.dll"
		(from the "Win32/" subdirectory) into:

		$JAVA_HOME\jre-VERSION\bin\

		(e.g. C:\Program Files\Java\jre1.5.0_07\bin\*)

	Note: $JAVA_HOME should be something like:
	
		C:\Program Files\Java\

